               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Loteprednol etabonate ophthalmic suspension is supplied in a plastic bottle with a controlled drop tip in the following sizes:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>NDC 68682-299-05    5 mL<br/>NDC 68682-299-10  10 mL<br/>NDC 68682-299-15  15 mL</paragraph>
                  <table width="100%">
                     <col width="100%"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <tr>
                           <td styleCode="Rrule Botrule Lrule Toprule " valign="top">
                              <paragraph>
                                 <content styleCode="bold">DO NOT USE IF NECKBAND IMPRINTED WITH "Protective Seal" AND YELLOW </content>
                                 <renderMultiMedia ID="id467" referencedObject="E0E68731-F5CC-460A-86F2-7D7C99C9E41D"/>
                                 <content styleCode="bold">IS NOT INTACT.</content>
                              </paragraph>
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                     </tbody>
                  </table>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20200501"/>
